    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age both inside and out. The engine starts up consistently and the car handles well on the road, but you should expect some minor cosmetic blemishes, interior wear, and the typical mechanical sounds of an older vehicle. It has been maintained enough to keep it roadworthy and dependable for commuting, making it a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a reasonable price.",
