    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly impeccable, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless original paint to the pristine interior, reflects its like-new status. Mechanically, it performs perfectly with no issues whatsoever, offering a driving experience identical to when it first left the dealership. This is a rare find for a collector or an enthusiast seeking the absolute best example of this model.",
