    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Exhibiting a consistent service history and exceptional mechanical integrity, the automobile delivers a refined and reliable driving experience. Every component has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and aesthetics. An authoritative choice for those seeking a high-caliber vehicle that balances sophistication with long-term utility.",
      "price": 34500.0,
